Pauley Perrette https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pauley_Perrette 0 Pauley Perrette (born March 27, 1969) is an American actress, best known for playing Abby Sciuto on the U.S. TV series NCIS. She is also a published writer, singer, and civil rights advocate. Pauley_Perrette ( born March_27_,_1969 ) is an_American_actress , best_known for playing Abby_Sciuto on the_U.S._TV_series_NCIS .
